  "instructions": [
    "Preheat tagine pot over medium heat and add olive oil.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until fragrant and translucent.",
    "Stir in fermented-jang, smoked paprika, cumin, and ginger, cooking for 1 minute to bloom spices.",
    "Add sliced beets, cover, and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and lemon juice, and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover and simmer for 25 minutes until beets are tender.",
    "Stir in lemon zest, season with salt and pepper to taste, and let cook for another 5 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat, fluff gently with a spoon, and transfer to a serving dish."
